{"name": "xy-configure", "metadata": {"name": "xy-configure", "version": "1.0.5", "classifiers": ["Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["xy-file"], "summary": "\u914d\u7f6e\u89e3\u6790\u6a21\u5757", "upload_time": 1731155307}, "documentation": ["<!--\n * @Author: yuyangit yuyangit.0515@qq.com\n * @Date: 2024-10-19 10:55:02\n * @LastEditors: yuyangit yuyangit.0515@qq.com\n * @LastEditTime: 2024-10-19 11:04:20\n * @FilePath: /xy_configure/README.md\n * @Description: \u8fd9\u662f\u9ed8\u8ba4\u8bbe\u7f6e,\u8bf7\u8bbe\u7f6e`customMade`, \u6253\u5f00koroFileHeader\u67e5\u770b\u914d\u7f6e \u8fdb\u884c\u8bbe\u7f6e: https://github.com/OBKoro1/koro1FileHeader/wiki/%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\n-->\n# xy_configure\n\n- [\u7b80\u4f53\u4e2d\u6587](./README.md)\n- [\u7e41\u9ad4\u4e2d\u6587](./README.zh-hant.md)\n- [English](./README.en.md)\n\n## \u8bf4\u660e\n\n\u901a\u7528\u914d\u7f6e\u6a21\u5757.\n\n\n## \u6e90\u7801\u4ed3\u5e93\n\n- <a href=\"https://github.com/xy-base/xy_configure.git\" target=\"_blank\">Github\u5730\u5740</a>  \n- <a href=\"https://gitee.com/xy-opensource/xy_configure.git\" target=\"_blank\">Gitee\u5730\u5740</a>  \n- <a href=\"https://gitcode.com/xy-opensource/xy_configure.git\" target=\"_blank\">GitCode\u5730\u5740</a>  \n\n## \u5b89\u88c5\n\n```bash\n# bash\npip install xy_configure\n```\n\n## \u4f7f\u7528\n\n```python\n# Python Interpreter.\nfrom xy_configure.Configure import Configure\nfrom xy_configure.Pair.Section import Section\nconfigure = Configure() \nconfigure['key_1'] = \"value_1\"\nconfigure[\"key_2\"] = \"value_2\"\nprint(configure)\n# {\"key_1\":\"value_1\", \"key_2\":\"value_2\"}\n\nconfigure = Configure() \nsection = Section()\nsection.set_value(\"key_1\",\"value_1\")\nconfigure.set_section(section)\nprint(configure)\n# {'SECTION': {'key_1': 'value_1'}}\nsection.set_name(\"section_1\")\nconfigure.set_section(section)\nprint(configure)\n# {'SECTION': {'key_1': 'value_1'}, 'section_1': {'key_1': 'value_1'}}\nconfigure.del_section(\"SECTION\")\nprint(configure)\n# {'section_1': {'key_1': 'value_1'}}\n\n```\n\n## \u8bb8\u53ef\u8bc1\nxy_configure \u6839\u636e <\u6728\u5170\u5bbd\u677e\u8bb8\u53ef\u8bc1, \u7b2c2\u7248> \u83b7\u5f97\u8bb8\u53ef\u3002\u6709\u5173\u8be6\u7ec6\u4fe1\u606f\uff0c\u8bf7\u53c2\u9605 [LICENSE](LICENSE) \u6587\u4ef6\u3002\n\n\n## \u6350\u8d60\n\n\u5982\u679c\u5c0f\u4f19\u4f34\u4eec\u89c9\u5f97\u8fd9\u4e9b\u5de5\u5177\u8fd8\u4e0d\u9519\u7684\u8bdd\uff0c\u80fd\u5426\u8bf7\u54b1\u559d\u4e00\u676f\u5496\u5561\u5462?  \n\n![Pay-Total](./readme/Pay-Total.png)\n\n\n## \u8054\u7cfb\u65b9\u5f0f\n\n```\n\u5fae\u4fe1: yuyangiit\n\u90ae\u7bb1: yuyangit.0515@qq.com\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "xy_configure", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": []}, {"name": "xy_configure.Pair.PairDelegate", "documentation": ["-*- coding: UTF-8 -*-"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "xy_configure.Pair.PairDelegate.__author__", "type": null, "documentation": ["* @File    :   PairDelegate.py\n* @Time    :   2023/04/23 14:09:10\n* @Author  :   \u4f59\u6d0b \n* @Version :   1.0\n* @Contact :   yuyangit.0515@qq.com\n* @License :   (C)Copyright 2019-2024, Ship of Ocean\n* @Desc    :   None"]}], "classes": [{"name": "xy_configure.Pair.PairDelegate.PairDelegate", "bases": ["ABCMeta"], "methods": [{"name": "xy_configure.Pair.PairDelegate.PairDelegate.should_set_value", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": {"name": "str | None", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "value", "type": null, "default": "..."}, {"name": "exist_ok", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "ok", "type": {"name": "bool", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bool", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": {"name": "bool", 